name: Suez Canal Girl
description:
Suez Canal Girl is a puzzle game mode, consisting of a different of nice game levels with Container Ship Girls. Exiting atmosphere, great SFX, levels with beautiful artworks.If you lover of hentai girls as container ships, this game is definitely for you!Thanks to our artists: Gekasso, KotaMota, Rino99

Amazing Suez Canal Girls, Nice Container Ships, Exciting Atmosphere, Great SFX, Levels with Beautiful Artworks.



Awesome for relax after a Hard Day at work at Suez Canal. Join us!

  • Unique game levels
  • Dynamic gameplay
  • Difficulty is increased with increasing levels
  • Exiting atmosphere
  • Great SFX
